###Block: Sorcerer Bloodlines
# Ability Name							Description
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Aberrant Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:There is a taint in your blood, one that is alien and bizarre. You tend to think in odd ways, approaching problems from an angle that most would not expect. Over time, this taint manifests itself in your physical form.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Abyssal Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Some time ago, a demon spread its filth into your heritage. While it does not manifest in all of your kin, for you it is  particularly strong, calling on you to bring ruin to those around you.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Arcane Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Your family has always been skilled in the art of magic. While many of your relatives were accomplished wizards, your powers developed without the need for study and practice.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Celestial Bloodline.MOD	DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Your bloodline is blessed by a celestial power, either through having a celestial relative or through divine intervention. Although this power drives you along the path of good, your fate is your own to determine.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Destined Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Your family is destined for greatness in some way. Your birth could have been foretold in prophecy, or perhaps it occurred during an especially auspicious event, such as a solar eclipse. Regardless of its origin, you have a great future ahead of you.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Draconic Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:At some point in your family's history, a dragon interbred with your bloodline, and now its ancient power flows through your veins.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Elemental Bloodline.MOD	DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:The power of the elements resides in you, and at times you can hardly control its fury. This influence comes from an elemental outsider in your family history or a time when you or your relatives were exposed to a powerful elemental force.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Fey Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:The capricious nature of the fey runs in your family due to some intermingling of fey blood or magic. This tends to make you more emotional than most, prone to bouts of extreme joy and rage.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Infernal Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Somewhere in your family's history, a relative made a deal with a devil, and that pact has influenced the line ever since. Now it manifests in direct and obvious ways, granting you powers and abilities. While your fate is still your own, you can't help but wonder if your ultimate reward is bound to the Pit.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Undead Bloodline.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:The touch of the grave runs through your family. Perhaps one of your ancestors became a powerful lich or vampire, or maybe you were born dead before suddenly returning to life. Either way, the forces of death move through you and touch your every action.

